text: I mean.  To be fair.  I live near the beach and there loads of parks.  It isn’t too bad. It’s just not nature. I lived in San Francisco and Yosemite is still one of my favourite places in the world.  Oh.  And Jarvis Bay in AU is also amazing.  The world is quite beautiful actually.
Ha.  Yah.  You can go from feeling perfectly fine to having the need to zip every zipper in a clothing store in no time. ...
